This is a list of [[public art]] in [[List of neighborhoods of the District of Columbia by ward|Ward 8]] of [[Washington, D.C.]].
This list applies only to works of [[public art]] accessible in an outdoor public space. For example, this does not include artwork visible inside a museum.
Most of the works mentioned are sculptures. When this is not the case (i.e. [[sound installation]], for example) it is stated next to the title. ==Ward 8==
